  "title": "SQL Server 2022",
  "contentHtml": "In this episode Michael sits down with Ajay Jagannathan&nbsp;\n                        (\n                           <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/ajayjag/'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>\n                        ) \n                        to talk about the recent release of SQL Server 2022 especially some of the new security features and hooks into Azure.\n      \n                        <br>\n                        We also discuss other SQL database security news.\n      \n                        <br><br>\n      \n                        <!-- Insert episode info from rss.com into NNNNNN and TTTTTT which is the episode number and the title -->\n                        <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/735488?theme=light\" class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"The Azure Security Podcast\" frameborder=\"0\"><a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/735488/\">SQL2022</a></iframe>\n      \n                        <h5>Links</h5> \n                        <!-- Links to news articles -->\n                        <ul>\n                           <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/735488/'>Transcript <i class=\"fa-solid fa-pencil\"></i></a></li>\n                           <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://public.cyber.mil/announcement/disa-releases-the-microsoft-azure-sql-database-security-technical-implementation-guide/#:~:text=The%20Defense%20Information%20Systems%20Agency%20recently%20approved%20the,Guide%20%28STIG%29%2C%20which%20is%20effective%20immediately%20upon%20release.\">DISA releases the Microsoft Azure SQL Database Security Technical Implementation Guide</a></li>\n                           <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/azure-sql-blog/troubleshooting-external-data-and-access-policies-in-azure-sql/ba-p/3683097\">Troubleshooting external data and access policies in Azure SQL and SQL Server</a></li>\n                           \n                           <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://cloudblogs.microsoft.com/sqlserver/2022/11/16/sql-server-2022-is-now-generally-available/\">SQL Server 2022 is now generally available</a></li>\n                           <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/sql-server/sql-server-2022\">Explore SQL Server 2022 capabilities</a></li>\n                           <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/sql/sql-server/what-s-new-in-sql-server-2022?view=sql-server-ver16\">What's new in SQL Server 2022</a></li>\n                           <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/sql/sql-server/what-s-new-in-sql-server-2022?view=sql-server-ver16#security\">What's new in SQL Server 2022: Security</a></li>\n                           <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://github.com/microsoft/bobsql/tree/master/demos/sqlserver2022\">SQL Server 2022 demos</a></li>\n                           <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://github.com/microsoft/sqlworkshops-sql2022workshop\">Workshop: The SQL Server 2022 Workshop</a></li>\n                           <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/training/modules/introduction-to-sql-server-2022/\">Introduction to SQL Server 2022</a></li>\n      \n                        </ul>"
